<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<title>Privacy Policy | TravelNest</title>

<div class="privacy-wrapper">
  <header class="privacy-header">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy matters. Learn how we handle your information at TravelNest.</p>
  </header>

  <main class="privacy-content container">
    <section>
      <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Name, email, phone number, profile details, payment information.</li>
        <li><strong>Booking Information:</strong> Reservation dates, property details, transaction records.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP addresses, device info, browsing activity, cookies.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>To process your bookings and provide customer support.</li>
        <li>To improve our services and personalize your experience.</li>
        <li>To communicate updates, offers (with your consent), and important information.</li>
        <li>To ensure security and prevent fraud.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Sharing Your Information</h3>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted third parties only to fulfill your requests, comply with laws, or protect our rights.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Cookies & Tracking</h3>
      <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience, analyze traffic, and provide tailored content. You can control cookie settings in your browser.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Your Rights</h3>
      <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data. Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@travelnest.com">support@travelnest.com</a> to exercise these rights.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Data Security</h3>
      <p>We adopt industry-standard security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. All changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@travelnest.com">support@travelnest.com</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>
